---
title: "Media Pipeline — Upload to Delivery"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User / Agent
    participant MM as media-manager
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant FS as Vault Storage
    participant VM as video-manager
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant A as Audience

    Note over U,A: Upload & Processing

    U->>MM: POST /api/media/upload<br/>(file + metadata)
    MM->>MC: Detect media type
    MC-->>MM: image / video / document
    MM->>DB: INSERT media_items (status: processing)
    MM->>FS: Write to vault/{vault_id}/media/{type}/
    MM-->>U: 202 Accepted + slug

    alt Video (MP4)
        U->>WS: Connect /api/media/{slug}/progress/ws
        MM->>VM: Spawn transcoding task
        loop 8-stage pipeline
            VM->>VM: Validate → Metadata → Transcode
            VM->>WS: Progress update (25-85%)
            VM->>VM: Thumbnail → Poster → DB → Cleanup
        end
        VM->>FS: Write HLS segments + master playlist
        VM->>DB: UPDATE status = active, video_type = hls
        VM->>WS: 100% complete
    else Image
        MM->>MM: Convert to WebP (cwebp)
        MM->>MM: Generate thumbnail
        MM->>FS: Write {slug}.webp + {slug}_thumb.webp
        MM->>DB: UPDATE status = active
    else Document (PDF)
        MM->>MM: Generate thumbnail (Ghostscript)
        MM->>FS: Write {slug}_thumb.webp
        MM->>DB: UPDATE status = active
    end

    Note over U,A: Delivery

    A->>MM: GET /media/{slug}/image.webp
    MM->>FS: Serve from vault
    MM-->>A: WebP image

    A->>MM: GET /hls/{slug}/index.m3u8
    MM->>FS: Serve HLS playlist
    MM-->>A: Adaptive streaming

    A->>MM: GET /media/{slug}/thumbnail
    MM->>FS: Serve thumbnail
    MM-->>A: Thumbnail WebP

    participant MC as media-core
